sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Admin or Security Guard
    participant UI as Event Device Screen
    participant Service as EventDeviceService
    participant DAO as DeviceDAO / EventDeviceDAO
    participant DB as Relational Database
    participant Monitor as MonitoringService

    User->>UI: Enter equipment, event, and approval document details
    UI->>Service: registerEventDevice(details)
    Service->>Service: Validate responsible person, event name, paper approval or signed GPOA, purpose, expected exit
    Service->>DAO: Save device and event details
    DAO->>DB: INSERT devices; INSERT event_devices
    Service-->>UI: Event device saved
    User->>UI: Log ingress/egress when equipment passes gate
    UI->>Monitor: logIngress/logEgress(eventDevice)
    Monitor->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE device_logs and campus_status
